title: PESJP Patch 2013 version 3.04 update
description:
*** PESJP Patch 2013 version 3.03 update ***



This is an update to PESJP Patch 2013 v3.0x



Apply update ONLY after:

1) first installing v3.0 - http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8195355/

2) and then installing update 3.02 - http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8214418/PESJP_Patch_2013_version_3.02_update




*** Update features ***
- Included update 3.03
- Fit DLC 4.00 (included)
- Update lastest player's stats & team formations
- Update some missing tranfers 
- Update PSD option file : correct boot for 2000 players
- Update face, hair, tattoo for some players    
- Gameplay tool 3.25
  -- Fixed XP incompatible issue in last version
  -- Update adboardserver : better quality texture, support 8bit, 24bit, 32bit     color png
  -- Added stadium & scoreboard preview :
- New option "Online compatible"
  -- Allow to use adboardserver, bannerserver, scoreboardserver, stadiumserver, chantserver while playing online
- Kitserver 13 prefinal
  -- Update faceserver & kitserver support online playing
